						<div class="postbody">i have an NES project where the mirroring is vertical, but I just realized the mirroring on my desired cartridge is horizontal. I looked over my documents but couldn't find info on this topic.<br />Basically what I'd like to know is if my project could keep it's vertical mirroring despite the above fact or if I have to tune and set up my code to handle horizontal mirroring before making a hard copy?<br /><br />Thanks for keeping these boards alive everyone! <img src="./images/smilies/Mfr_icon_homebrew.png" alt=":beer:" title="Beer" /></div>

