				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Whether nametable mirroring is hardwired depends on the cart type (mapper). On NROM, UxROM etc the mirroring is hardwired, on AxROM, MMC1, MMC3 it's mapper controllable.<br /><br />That said, you can rewire the cart to switch to vertical mirroring, see <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/rom.txt">http://nesdev.com/rom.txt</a><!-- m --> for details. CIRAM A10 is the key.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 85%; line-height: normal">Download STREEMERZ for NES from <a href="http://www.fauxgame.com" class="postlink">www.fauxgame.com</a>!</span></div>
					<br clear="all" /><br />

